WEBVTT

01:26.640 --> 01:34.960
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.600 --> 01:37.680
[Episode 6]

01:41.789 --> 01:43.590
Have you seen the mother and son?

01:45.680 --> 01:46.940
Did Chen Yan ask you...

01:47.090 --> 01:48.620
to pass on any message to me?

01:52.800 --> 01:53.660
No, she didn't.

01:56.590 --> 01:57.850
Tie, I'm here this time

01:58.600 --> 02:00.390
for my own business.

02:01.810 --> 02:03.940
I'm staying at Seasons Change Hostel.

02:08.860 --> 02:09.910
Oh, that matter!

02:11.860 --> 02:12.350
Yo, Bro.

02:12.780 --> 02:14.130
That was what you wanted to talk about?

02:14.130 --> 02:15.180
You making such a big deal out of it

02:15.180 --> 02:16.150
scared me.

02:19.079 --> 02:20.780
You're staying
at Seasons Change Hostel too?

02:20.780 --> 02:21.420
Yeah.

02:21.910 --> 02:22.610
Bro, I...

02:22.680 --> 02:24.020
I just arrived in Beijing.

02:24.020 --> 02:24.690
Seasons Change Hostel

02:24.690 --> 02:26.420
was the first place I stayed at.

02:26.530 --> 02:28.329
I treat it like home,

02:28.590 --> 02:29.720
and the people there

02:29.800 --> 02:30.860
are like my family.

02:30.910 --> 02:32.400
Many of them have already paid

02:32.400 --> 02:33.960
several months of rent.

02:34.340 --> 02:36.130
Kicking them out now

02:36.130 --> 02:37.410
wouldn't be right.

02:37.520 --> 02:38.590
It has to be first come, first served.

02:38.590 --> 02:40.390
We have to be reasonable, right?

02:44.030 --> 02:44.760
Reasonable?

02:47.020 --> 02:48.610
I'm not capable of that.

02:51.500 --> 02:52.100
Young man,

02:52.520 --> 02:54.960
you're much better than those three.

02:55.650 --> 02:57.579
They were just straight-up lying.

02:58.400 --> 02:59.600
You came to talk to me,

02:59.870 --> 03:00.690
all straightforward.

03:00.690 --> 03:02.090
I like your personality.

03:02.840 --> 03:04.370
What? Are you their boss?

03:04.430 --> 03:04.960
No.

03:05.780 --> 03:07.600
There's no such thing

03:07.740 --> 03:08.250
there.

03:08.900 --> 03:10.560
We come from all over the country.

03:10.560 --> 03:12.490
We're all here to chase our dreams.

03:12.520 --> 03:13.020
Dreams!

03:15.370 --> 03:16.550
We're unlike you.

03:17.190 --> 03:18.740
When you first came to Beijing,

03:18.740 --> 03:20.070
you had so much capital.

03:25.180 --> 03:26.579
You're close to Chen Yan.

03:27.650 --> 03:29.079
I'm doing this for her sake.

03:29.079 --> 03:29.740
How's that?

03:30.079 --> 03:31.520
If you want to eat here,

03:32.180 --> 03:32.960
then stay.

03:33.780 --> 03:34.750
If you don't,

03:35.530 --> 03:36.079
get out.

03:40.560 --> 03:41.910
Get lost.

03:41.930 --> 03:43.190
Don't you understand?

03:43.210 --> 03:43.780
Get lost!

03:44.030 --> 03:45.180
-Don't touch me.
-Go. Get out.

03:45.180 --> 03:45.960
Don't touch me.

03:45.960 --> 03:46.860
-Get out!
-Don't touch me.

03:46.860 --> 03:47.870
Let me say one last thing!

03:47.870 --> 03:49.000
You talk too much.

03:50.410 --> 03:52.030
This is for your ears only.

03:53.710 --> 03:54.650
Come, come.

03:54.650 --> 03:55.070
Speak!

03:55.620 --> 03:56.310
Let go.

04:10.240 --> 04:12.280
When Chen Yan was pregnant,

04:13.120 --> 04:15.150
you made money
through ways you shouldn't have.

04:15.150 --> 04:17.250
That guy is still looking for you.

04:30.830 --> 04:32.159
What are you looking at?

04:32.420 --> 04:33.680
You don't know who I am?

04:43.440 --> 04:45.050
You dared to come to me alone.

04:45.750 --> 04:47.350
I respect you for being a man.

04:49.750 --> 04:51.770
But as for the Seasons Change Hostel—

04:51.770 --> 04:53.170
I will go, no matter what.

04:57.870 --> 04:58.720
I'll go with you.

04:58.720 --> 04:59.920
No need. You guys eat.

05:10.450 --> 05:12.180
If I don't settle this today,

05:12.980 --> 05:14.310
I'm going to Wenzhou!

05:23.030 --> 05:25.290
Fine! I'll send you to Wenzhou right now!

05:31.630 --> 05:32.130
Come on!

05:32.570 --> 05:33.500
Really leaving?

05:33.830 --> 05:34.270
I'm leaving.

05:34.270 --> 05:34.800
Bye, Luo.

05:34.800 --> 05:36.010
-Take care.
-You've got everything.

05:36.010 --> 05:36.640
Got it all.

05:36.670 --> 05:37.470
Take care.

05:37.600 --> 05:38.220
Bye, Luo.

05:41.750 --> 05:42.750
Everyone's gone.

05:43.240 --> 05:44.300
It's just us left.

05:46.159 --> 05:46.770
In the end,

05:46.770 --> 05:48.000
it's just us left.

05:49.470 --> 05:51.400
All good things must come to an end.

05:51.740 --> 05:52.750
I advise you guys

05:53.360 --> 05:54.890
to find a new place quickly.

05:55.870 --> 05:56.560
If you ever

05:56.560 --> 05:58.000
miss me, Little Northeasterner,

05:58.000 --> 05:59.130
come back and see me.

05:59.220 --> 06:00.750
As long as the Seasons Change Hostel's sign

06:00.750 --> 06:01.550
is still here,

06:01.720 --> 06:02.570
I, Little Northeasterner,

06:02.570 --> 06:04.930
will still be right here
waiting for everyone.

06:04.930 --> 06:05.660
Liangliang.

06:06.180 --> 06:07.640
Have you found a place yet?

06:07.920 --> 06:08.460
No.

06:09.010 --> 06:10.660
There's a place that's free.

06:12.300 --> 06:12.860
Free?

06:13.000 --> 06:14.450
Have you seen Mr. Xu?

06:16.920 --> 06:17.890
Probably ran away.

06:17.890 --> 06:19.730
He wouldn't run even if you did.

06:20.000 --> 06:21.660
His stuff is still in the room.

06:21.770 --> 06:22.390
He probably

06:22.390 --> 06:23.980
just didn't have time to pack.

06:23.980 --> 06:26.180
He probably fled in panic.

06:30.060 --> 06:30.990
Where is Ranran?

06:32.650 --> 06:33.710
Crying in the room.

06:33.800 --> 06:34.800
Why is she crying?

06:36.740 --> 06:37.430
I need to go check on her.

06:37.430 --> 06:38.230
Go have a look.

06:41.450 --> 06:45.250
Today, we drink the celebration wine.

06:46.560 --> 06:50.240
I vow never to rest until my goal is met.

06:50.240 --> 06:54.620
The future is long for us
to show our skills.

06:56.040 --> 06:57.250
Willing—

07:02.270 --> 07:03.400
Where is Xu Shengli?

07:04.620 --> 07:05.710
Feng Tieyou.

07:05.810 --> 07:07.350
Didn't we have a deal?

07:07.830 --> 07:08.890
For the remaining tenants,

07:08.890 --> 07:09.930
give them a few more days.

07:09.930 --> 07:10.450
Once they find a place,

07:10.450 --> 07:11.450
they'll move out.

07:11.830 --> 07:12.960
You promised me too.

07:13.300 --> 07:14.250
Why are you here again?

07:14.250 --> 07:15.670
Is there no end to this?

07:15.720 --> 07:16.190
It's the middle of the night.

07:16.190 --> 07:17.720
What act are you putting on?

07:19.040 --> 07:20.160
Stop wasting your breath.

07:20.160 --> 07:21.290
Where is Xu Shengli?

07:26.720 --> 07:27.580
You don't know?

07:29.950 --> 07:30.760
I do.

07:35.220 --> 07:36.070
Xu Shengli!

07:37.360 --> 07:39.230
Xu Shengli!

07:41.330 --> 07:42.900
Xu Shengli!

07:46.300 --> 07:47.180
Xu Shengli.

07:48.010 --> 07:48.930
From today on,

07:48.930 --> 07:50.210
Xu Shengli is my bro!

07:51.300 --> 07:53.850
I really didn't scare you today.

07:54.000 --> 07:55.180
If he had died today,

07:55.190 --> 07:56.680
I would have had to pay with my life.

07:56.680 --> 07:57.890
If he had been crippled,

07:57.890 --> 07:59.690
I would have been sentenced too!

07:59.920 --> 08:01.180
What's the date today?

08:01.190 --> 08:02.000
Doesn't matter.

08:02.000 --> 08:03.110
This day next year

08:03.180 --> 08:04.680
will be the death anniversary
for us brothers.

08:04.680 --> 08:05.280
No, no, no.

08:05.430 --> 08:06.600
What death anniversary?

08:06.600 --> 08:07.600
Oh, no, I misspoke.

08:07.600 --> 08:09.270
It'd be our anniversary.

08:11.420 --> 08:12.360
What's going on?

08:14.450 --> 08:14.980
No big deal.

08:14.980 --> 08:15.420
Well,

08:15.450 --> 08:17.630
you are all his...

08:18.000 --> 08:18.930
buddies, right?

08:21.300 --> 08:22.760
There's a pretty lady here too.

08:22.760 --> 08:23.430
Sis.

08:23.690 --> 08:24.450
Actually,

08:24.450 --> 08:26.180
Officer Tang from the police station

08:26.180 --> 08:27.170
talked to me too.

08:27.240 --> 08:28.610
Starting today, you

08:28.680 --> 08:29.450
don't have to leave.

08:29.450 --> 08:30.980
Just stay here and make art.

08:31.600 --> 08:32.110
Well,

08:32.110 --> 08:32.720
Little Northeasterner,

08:32.720 --> 08:33.429
lately,

08:33.530 --> 08:35.130
I've made a real mess of things for you.

08:35.130 --> 08:35.750
I'm sorry.

08:35.860 --> 08:36.559
Okay?

08:36.840 --> 08:38.030
Let's forget the past!

08:38.030 --> 08:39.500
We'll wipe the slate clean today.

08:39.500 --> 08:41.030
Let's start fresh tomorrow.

08:41.030 --> 08:42.320
You guys are my bros,

08:42.440 --> 08:42.900
and sis.

08:42.960 --> 08:43.549
Okay?

08:43.580 --> 08:44.710
The power is back on.

08:45.600 --> 08:46.210
Sorry.

08:46.410 --> 08:47.540
The water situation

08:48.100 --> 08:49.390
has nothing to do with me.

08:49.390 --> 08:49.820
Sorry.

08:50.130 --> 08:51.130
I'm really sorry.

08:51.270 --> 08:52.440
Just make do for one more night,

08:52.440 --> 08:52.890
okay?

08:53.030 --> 08:54.630
Then how do I take a shower...

08:57.120 --> 08:58.160
That's that, Shengli.

08:58.160 --> 08:59.670
I don't know if I made myself clear.

08:59.670 --> 09:00.390
You made yourself clear!

09:00.390 --> 09:00.870
I did?

09:00.870 --> 09:01.320
Bro.

09:03.200 --> 09:04.100
From now on,

09:04.370 --> 09:05.370
this is your home.

09:05.480 --> 09:06.670
You're always welcome

09:06.670 --> 09:07.910
at Seasons Change Hostel.

09:07.910 --> 09:08.640
Am I?

09:08.670 --> 09:09.790
Of course!

09:10.980 --> 09:11.320
Okay!

09:11.840 --> 09:12.650
That's great!

09:14.840 --> 09:15.970
Section Chief Wang!

09:21.580 --> 09:22.250
Sis.

09:22.290 --> 09:24.150
Just think of me as a crazy person.

09:24.940 --> 09:26.000
All right, I'm leaving.

09:26.000 --> 09:26.630
I'm off.

09:27.530 --> 09:28.410
We're all family now.

09:28.410 --> 09:29.390
Stay here tonight.

09:29.390 --> 09:30.620
Let's have a drink together.

09:30.620 --> 09:31.290
Stay here?

09:32.650 --> 09:34.000
No, he meant...

09:34.120 --> 09:35.010
M-Maybe not today.

09:35.010 --> 09:36.410
Let's drink another day.

09:39.120 --> 09:39.780
Walk me out.

09:40.250 --> 09:40.870
Well...

09:41.270 --> 09:41.910
Shengli.

09:42.650 --> 09:43.780
Making it in Beijing

09:43.840 --> 09:44.510
isn't easy.

09:45.010 --> 09:46.870
You're here to chase your dreams.

09:47.480 --> 09:48.290
Well,

09:48.960 --> 09:49.410
if...

09:51.030 --> 09:52.220
if anyone bullies you,

09:52.220 --> 09:52.950
just tell me.

09:53.460 --> 09:53.870
Okay.

09:55.770 --> 09:57.050
I shouldn't be telling you this.

09:57.050 --> 09:57.910
All these years

09:58.720 --> 10:00.780
Chen Yan and I have been divorced for,

10:01.320 --> 10:03.050
she wouldn't let me see the kid.

10:04.150 --> 10:05.990
And I still miss the kid.

10:10.030 --> 10:12.150
We just have different personalities.

10:12.150 --> 10:13.370
We fight every time we meet.

10:13.370 --> 10:14.440
Every single time.

10:15.000 --> 10:16.730
She wouldn't let me see the kid.

10:18.030 --> 10:20.490
You two just have different personalities.

10:22.510 --> 10:22.940
Bro,

10:24.010 --> 10:25.580
I... I'm young.

10:25.820 --> 10:27.550
I might be speaking out of turn.

10:28.620 --> 10:29.890
But I think

10:29.890 --> 10:31.750
what Chen Yan needs most right now

10:34.270 --> 10:35.410
is a good husband.

10:36.500 --> 10:37.960
And what the kid needs most

10:40.660 --> 10:41.720
is a good father.

10:43.650 --> 10:44.750
I can help you.

10:44.750 --> 10:45.800
I can.

10:48.130 --> 10:49.260
But for this matter,

10:50.750 --> 10:52.210
you have to do it yourself.

10:56.550 --> 10:58.460
I'm learning things from you instead.

10:58.460 --> 10:59.610
No, no.

10:59.740 --> 11:01.030
I'm nobody.

11:01.620 --> 11:03.020
But I think you're right.

11:06.150 --> 11:06.680
Shengli.

11:07.960 --> 11:09.140
You'll definitely

11:09.580 --> 11:11.120
become a great screenwriter.

11:11.120 --> 11:12.180
I have faith in you!

11:14.150 --> 11:14.610
Really?

11:14.890 --> 11:15.500
Really!

11:21.220 --> 11:23.410
A great screenwriter.

11:25.050 --> 11:25.720
Shengli.

11:27.790 --> 11:29.160
Slow down, slow down.

11:30.010 --> 11:31.820
What's going on?

11:36.720 --> 11:37.500
That's how

11:38.580 --> 11:39.640
the script went...

11:46.820 --> 11:48.220
I'll give you one more chance.

11:48.220 --> 11:49.480
Are you going to dodge?

11:50.580 --> 11:51.320
Come on!

12:12.300 --> 12:13.300
What's your name?

12:13.860 --> 12:14.710
Xu Shengli.

12:23.800 --> 12:25.790
A humble meal—
just a small token of respect.

12:25.790 --> 12:26.540
If it weren't

12:26.650 --> 12:28.010
for Xu this time,

12:28.320 --> 12:30.770
my little Seasons Change Hostel

12:30.840 --> 12:32.310
wouldn't have survived to the next season.

12:32.310 --> 12:33.140
Thank you, Xu.

12:33.530 --> 12:33.960
Xu,

12:34.550 --> 12:36.410
I'd like to propose a toast to you.

12:37.080 --> 12:37.540
Come on.

12:37.590 --> 12:39.320
We'll drink three to one glass.

12:39.360 --> 12:39.870
Come on.

12:39.870 --> 12:41.050
I-I'll finish mine.

12:41.050 --> 12:41.700
Come on.

12:41.700 --> 12:43.030
Then I'll finish mine too.

12:43.030 --> 12:44.820
Come on.

12:45.460 --> 12:46.210
Thank you.

12:50.580 --> 12:51.310
Refreshing!

12:52.050 --> 12:53.500
It's nothing.

12:53.500 --> 12:54.800
We have a long future ahead of us.

12:54.800 --> 12:55.370
Right.

12:55.700 --> 12:57.080
There's a long future ahead.

12:57.080 --> 12:58.590
This time, we can say

12:58.670 --> 12:59.890
we faced a disaster together.

12:59.890 --> 13:01.220
I saw that everyone here

13:01.600 --> 13:02.620
has such backbone

13:02.940 --> 13:04.000
and such courage.

13:04.200 --> 13:05.330
You are all real men.

13:05.580 --> 13:07.510
To be honest, the anger I had before

13:07.510 --> 13:08.710
has pretty much dissipated.

13:08.710 --> 13:09.670
Still angry, huh?

13:09.670 --> 13:10.360
No, no. No anger.

13:10.360 --> 13:11.400
It's gone now.

13:11.940 --> 13:12.670
We all

13:12.670 --> 13:15.130
come from
different corners of the country.

13:15.410 --> 13:16.940
We all have our own character

13:16.940 --> 13:18.150
and our own temper.

13:18.290 --> 13:18.600
Right.

13:18.600 --> 13:20.100
We didn't know each other before,

13:20.100 --> 13:22.430
so a little friction is perfectly normal.

13:22.440 --> 13:23.070
But,

13:24.030 --> 13:26.260
there's always a way to solve it.

13:26.460 --> 13:27.920
Like my sleeping habits—

13:28.020 --> 13:29.390
snoring and grinding my teeth.

13:29.390 --> 13:29.960
I asked!

13:30.030 --> 13:30.790
I asked the doctor!

13:30.790 --> 13:31.910
The doctor said it can be cured.

13:31.910 --> 13:32.470
-Really?
-Really?

13:32.470 --> 13:33.700
Anyway, in a nutshell,

13:33.700 --> 13:34.940
what happened in the past

13:34.940 --> 13:35.740
is in the past.

13:35.860 --> 13:36.520
From now on,

13:37.150 --> 13:38.120
let's be close—

13:38.270 --> 13:38.930
real close.

13:39.100 --> 13:39.450
Yes.

13:39.480 --> 13:40.780
Let's treat each other like family.

13:40.780 --> 13:41.410
Yes, yes.

13:41.410 --> 13:42.390
Xu, say no more.

13:42.410 --> 13:43.980
After this, we move on.

13:44.000 --> 13:44.700
-Let's move on.
-Let's move on.

13:44.700 --> 13:46.050
-Let's move on.
-Let's move on. Come on!

13:46.050 --> 13:47.050
Come on, drink up.

13:47.050 --> 13:47.750
Don't down it.

13:47.750 --> 13:48.670
Take it slow.

13:48.700 --> 13:49.670
So lively here.

13:50.820 --> 13:52.150
Started drinking without waiting for us?

13:52.150 --> 13:53.980
We went to your room,
but no one was there.

13:53.980 --> 13:54.570
Come on.

13:54.600 --> 13:55.200
Come on.

13:55.770 --> 13:57.650
Adding a dish for our hero here.

13:58.630 --> 13:59.390
Thanks.

13:59.390 --> 14:00.530
This glass hasn't been used.

14:00.530 --> 14:00.860
Okay.

14:00.860 --> 14:01.880
-Chopsticks. Chopsticks.
-Sit down.

14:01.880 --> 14:03.310
What a beautiful sight.

14:03.360 --> 14:04.080
You two sit next to each other.

14:04.080 --> 14:04.960
-Come on.
-Come on.

14:04.960 --> 14:05.480
Here.

14:05.600 --> 14:07.130
I hope I'm not interrupting.

14:07.130 --> 14:08.150
-No.
-No.

14:08.480 --> 14:10.410
We were going to invite you anyway.

14:10.820 --> 14:12.220
Wh-Why am I sitting here?

14:12.340 --> 14:13.080
Move over!

14:13.410 --> 14:14.440
No need!

14:14.440 --> 14:16.030
Just move.

14:16.480 --> 14:17.610
My back is acting up.

14:18.460 --> 14:18.940
All right.

14:18.940 --> 14:20.000
You sure are sharp.

14:20.750 --> 14:22.510
You really weren't scared yesterday?

14:22.510 --> 14:23.340
Those guys looked like

14:23.340 --> 14:24.600
they don't fear death.

14:24.960 --> 14:27.170
I didn't even think about being scared.

14:27.240 --> 14:28.270
I was totally stunned.

14:28.270 --> 14:29.010
I hadn't decided

14:29.010 --> 14:30.360
whether to dodge left or right,

14:30.360 --> 14:32.090
and the car just whooshed past.

14:32.370 --> 14:33.580
You're an honest guy.

14:33.650 --> 14:34.250
Right?

14:34.290 --> 14:35.020
But

14:35.050 --> 14:36.800
fortune favors fools.

14:37.270 --> 14:37.870
If it were me,

14:37.870 --> 14:39.010
whichever way I dodged,

14:39.010 --> 14:39.960
the car would crash that way.

14:39.960 --> 14:41.620
I would have been sent flying.

14:43.440 --> 14:43.820
Here.

14:45.360 --> 14:46.090
What's this?

14:46.290 --> 14:47.480
Someone from the Student Union
gave them to me.

14:47.480 --> 14:48.080
Let me see.

14:48.130 --> 14:48.460
Here.

14:49.600 --> 14:50.390
Yesterday I helped them

14:50.390 --> 14:51.580
guide an event all day,

14:51.580 --> 14:53.110
so they gave me two tickets.

14:53.750 --> 14:55.620
Vouchers for the Central TV & Radio Tower
trial run.

14:55.620 --> 14:56.890
If you sell them to scalpers,

14:56.890 --> 14:58.000
you could make a couple hundred.

14:58.000 --> 14:59.980
Why do you have
to make money on everything?

14:59.980 --> 15:02.120
Young people should enjoy themselves.

15:02.120 --> 15:03.250
Go up and have a look.

15:03.700 --> 15:05.080
Every time I pass by there,

15:05.080 --> 15:06.080
I think to myself,

15:06.220 --> 15:08.200
how is this tower so tall?

15:08.700 --> 15:09.440
People say

15:09.580 --> 15:10.640
that from up there,

15:10.670 --> 15:13.210
you can see the whole of Beijing.

15:13.480 --> 15:13.980
You can.

15:14.150 --> 15:15.050
Yes, you can see it.

15:15.050 --> 15:15.650
Right?

15:16.600 --> 15:17.550
But these are worth a lot.

15:17.550 --> 15:18.580
Why don't you sell them?

15:18.580 --> 15:19.510
You can make some money too.

15:19.510 --> 15:20.720
I want to go.

15:23.050 --> 15:23.800
Then go.

15:28.510 --> 15:29.420
Drink up.

15:29.860 --> 15:30.600
Come on.

15:30.630 --> 15:31.290
Count me in.

15:31.740 --> 15:32.340
What?

15:32.340 --> 15:34.410
-You two just go.
-Come on. Here.

15:34.720 --> 15:35.630
Here.

15:35.630 --> 15:36.200
Let's clink glasses!

15:36.200 --> 15:36.730
Cheers.

15:36.840 --> 15:39.050
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

15:44.410 --> 15:45.650
It's so tall!

15:46.010 --> 15:47.120
How high is this?

15:48.150 --> 15:48.890
Are we going

15:48.890 --> 15:50.030
to the very top later?

15:50.030 --> 15:50.860
Of course.

15:52.850 --> 15:54.480
Haven't you been here before?

15:54.480 --> 15:55.080
No.

15:55.370 --> 15:57.220
Didn't you come to Beijing before?

15:57.220 --> 15:58.360
You've never been up?

15:58.360 --> 15:58.950
Nope.

16:00.320 --> 16:01.320
Are you afraid of heights?

16:01.320 --> 16:02.690
Of course not.

16:03.130 --> 16:03.890
Why? Are you scared?

16:03.890 --> 16:05.390
I'm not scared.

16:06.620 --> 16:07.190
Okay.

16:07.720 --> 16:09.320
Whoever gets scared is a dog.

16:10.940 --> 16:11.490
Let's go!

16:11.790 --> 16:12.320
Let's go!

16:14.150 --> 16:15.010
Welcome

16:15.010 --> 16:16.340
everyone who's here to visit

16:16.340 --> 16:17.550
the Central TV & Radio Tower.

16:17.550 --> 16:18.700
Since this is

16:18.700 --> 16:19.740
a high-speed elevator,

16:19.740 --> 16:21.550
your ears might feel uncomfortable

16:21.550 --> 16:22.890
during the ride.

16:22.960 --> 16:24.820
You can swallow

16:24.820 --> 16:26.220
to relieve the pressure.

16:33.630 --> 16:34.290
This works.

16:41.010 --> 16:41.870
My ears popped.

16:42.600 --> 16:43.910
We have arrived. Please alight slowly.

16:43.910 --> 16:45.100
Watch your step.

16:46.010 --> 16:47.270
Hello. Welcome.

16:47.340 --> 16:49.510
We're at the Open-Air Observation Deck.

16:49.510 --> 16:51.510
Mind the steps. Watch your footing.

16:53.410 --> 16:54.400
It's huge!

16:56.620 --> 16:58.200
Come on. Let's go check over there.

16:58.200 --> 16:58.620
Okay.

16:58.870 --> 16:59.730
Zhuang Zhuang!

17:02.790 --> 17:03.540
What is this?

17:03.630 --> 17:04.530
A telescope.

17:06.720 --> 17:07.349
It's so clear.

17:07.349 --> 17:09.160
There are people dancing over there!

17:09.160 --> 17:09.700
Where?

17:10.460 --> 17:11.119
Over there.

17:11.170 --> 17:11.869
Have a look.

17:12.480 --> 17:13.579
Let me try.

17:13.579 --> 17:14.839
You can see really far.

17:17.250 --> 17:18.810
There's nothing; it's dark.

17:18.810 --> 17:19.609
There's nothing?

17:19.609 --> 17:20.140
No—

17:24.010 --> 17:24.940
Here, let me see.

17:27.460 --> 17:28.500
Look down there!

17:29.090 --> 17:29.690
Bayi Lake!

17:30.610 --> 17:31.980
Next to Bayi Lake!

17:32.050 --> 17:32.700
Where?

17:33.400 --> 17:34.500
The Military Museum!

17:34.500 --> 17:34.900
Look.

17:35.690 --> 17:36.900
To the right of the lake.

17:36.900 --> 17:38.100
The Military Museum.

17:38.690 --> 17:39.370
Do you see it?

17:39.370 --> 17:40.470
Where is the museum?

17:40.470 --> 17:41.330
To the right of that lake.

17:41.330 --> 17:42.250
Go right a bit.

17:43.140 --> 17:44.340
The Military Museum.

17:45.090 --> 17:46.310
Go up. Further up.

17:47.310 --> 17:48.240
In the distance.

17:48.840 --> 17:49.500
That row

17:49.520 --> 17:50.680
of yellow roofs

17:50.810 --> 17:51.400
is the Forbidden City.

17:51.400 --> 17:53.000
Look further left.

17:53.100 --> 17:54.500
A little more to the left.

17:55.040 --> 17:56.350
White Pagoda Temple. Do you see it?

17:56.350 --> 17:57.050
I see it.

17:57.240 --> 17:58.640
Further past the White Pagoda Temple

17:58.640 --> 17:59.440
is our home.

18:00.550 --> 18:01.900
Little Northeasterner is riding a bike

18:01.900 --> 18:02.610
right into the house.

18:02.610 --> 18:03.870
You still can't see it?

18:04.740 --> 18:06.270
Since when is it "our home"?

18:07.840 --> 18:10.150
That... That is our home.

18:10.680 --> 18:12.010
Seasons Change Hostel.

18:14.000 --> 18:15.180
You say "our home"

18:15.180 --> 18:16.110
so naturally.

18:17.050 --> 18:17.510
That...

18:17.850 --> 18:18.720
That's...

18:19.060 --> 18:20.480
a home for all of us.

18:22.570 --> 18:23.700
You sound so guilty.

18:24.550 --> 18:25.900
How so?

18:26.850 --> 18:28.380
Let me take a picture of you.

18:28.420 --> 18:29.290
You brought a camera?

18:29.290 --> 18:30.560
I did!

18:37.330 --> 18:37.790
Come on.

18:39.070 --> 18:41.870
One, two, three.

18:42.500 --> 18:42.830
Great.

18:42.830 --> 18:44.030
Let me take one of you.

18:44.090 --> 18:44.610
Okay.

18:44.680 --> 18:45.680
You look so happy!

18:46.010 --> 18:46.830
Let me take a photo

18:46.830 --> 18:47.940
of you two newlyweds.

18:47.940 --> 18:48.550
It'll be ready in an instant!

18:48.550 --> 18:49.600
What newlyweds?

18:49.850 --> 18:51.250
We're just good friends.

18:51.960 --> 18:53.130
All the more
you should take a photo together.

18:53.130 --> 18:54.110
It's so beautiful here.

18:54.110 --> 18:54.960
Take a picture for a keepsake!

18:54.960 --> 18:55.640
Come on.

18:55.940 --> 18:56.850
-Come on.
-We can get the photo

18:56.850 --> 18:58.030
after you take it?

18:58.460 --> 18:59.570
You can get it instantly here.

18:59.570 --> 19:01.130
How can film be instant?

19:01.610 --> 19:02.210
This here

19:02.230 --> 19:03.200
is the latest technology.

19:03.200 --> 19:04.380
I spent a fortune on it.

19:04.380 --> 19:05.210
It's a digital camera.

19:05.210 --> 19:05.940
How about it?

19:06.570 --> 19:07.500
Well then...

19:08.500 --> 19:09.060
Let's take one.

19:09.060 --> 19:09.630
Come on.

19:09.700 --> 19:11.220
-Come on. Come on.
-Closer. Closer.

19:11.220 --> 19:11.950
Great.

19:12.200 --> 19:13.000
Smile.

19:13.020 --> 19:14.220
Miss, give us a smile.

19:14.480 --> 19:16.330
Okay. Three, two, one.

19:17.150 --> 19:17.680
Okay.

19:17.850 --> 19:19.110
Beijing welcomes you.

19:19.330 --> 19:19.980
How much?

19:21.640 --> 19:22.110
Twenty.

19:23.150 --> 19:24.280
Twenty?

19:24.370 --> 19:25.700
That's way too expensive.

19:25.700 --> 19:26.630
It's instant.

19:26.650 --> 19:27.850
We'll think about it.

19:28.420 --> 19:29.530
-It's too expensive.
-Hey!

19:29.530 --> 19:30.830
Can you make it cheaper?

19:30.830 --> 19:33.030
-We don't want it.
-I'll keep it for you.

19:47.700 --> 19:49.430
You can even eat here?

19:49.960 --> 19:50.520
Look.

19:51.610 --> 19:53.410
This is a revolving restaurant?

19:54.140 --> 19:55.920
It rotates once every 90 minutes.

19:55.920 --> 19:57.240
You can see all of Beijing.

19:57.240 --> 19:58.100
How do you know?

19:58.440 --> 20:00.100
It's mentioned on the ticket.

20:02.030 --> 20:03.830
It doesn't look like it's turning.

20:03.830 --> 20:05.110
Is... Is it expensive?

20:06.880 --> 20:08.940
We can't afford it right now, anyway.

20:10.080 --> 20:11.480
Maybe when we have money.

20:25.790 --> 20:26.720
It's rock-hard.

20:28.080 --> 20:28.940
It is a bit hard.

20:34.800 --> 20:36.260
I'm going to the restroom.

20:36.630 --> 20:37.460
Wait for me.

20:38.380 --> 20:39.250
I'll be quick.

21:31.670 --> 21:32.790
Beijing is great.

21:36.920 --> 21:38.320
Let's work hard

21:39.250 --> 21:41.640
to stay in this city!

21:48.720 --> 21:50.180
Mr. Zheng said I can't shout.

21:50.180 --> 21:51.310
I have to protect my voice.

21:51.310 --> 21:52.640
Then I'll shout for you.

21:54.420 --> 21:57.880
Zhuang Zhuang is going to stay too!

22:11.010 --> 22:12.670
[Central TV & Radio Tower;
altitude: 405 meters]

22:14.700 --> 22:15.500
You bought it?

22:16.740 --> 22:18.400
Twenty yuan is too expensive.

22:18.980 --> 22:19.500
Forty.

22:27.140 --> 22:29.410
[Central TV & Radio Tower;
altitude: 405 meters]

22:31.980 --> 22:34.910
You could have spent this money
on something better.

22:50.660 --> 22:52.120
You're finally here, Cui.

22:52.400 --> 22:54.400
Your dialect is slipping out again.

22:54.970 --> 22:56.410
I'm just anxious.

22:56.640 --> 22:58.180
I'll be careful next time.

22:58.240 --> 23:00.030
I won't make the same mistake again.

23:00.030 --> 23:00.750
Look.

23:01.270 --> 23:02.180
This outfit you're wearing today,

23:02.180 --> 23:03.010
it looks so good.

23:03.010 --> 23:03.590
On the day of the audition,

23:03.590 --> 23:04.990
why didn't you wear this?

23:08.140 --> 23:08.830
Ranran.

23:09.240 --> 23:11.030
I told you over the phone.

23:11.330 --> 23:12.400
The director has already

23:12.400 --> 23:13.350
cast all the roles.

23:13.350 --> 23:15.350
There's really no chance this time.

23:16.660 --> 23:17.590
Can't you help me

23:17.590 --> 23:18.850
figure something out?

23:18.960 --> 23:19.330
Well,

23:19.810 --> 23:20.660
if there was a way,

23:20.660 --> 23:22.790
wouldn't I help you?

23:26.070 --> 23:27.260
Don't cry.

23:27.640 --> 23:28.440
Tell you what.

23:28.680 --> 23:29.720
Let's wait.

23:29.760 --> 23:30.350
Okay?

23:30.740 --> 23:32.500
In case something goes wrong with a role,

23:32.500 --> 23:33.030
or an actor

23:33.030 --> 23:34.220
gets a stomachache and can't come,

23:34.220 --> 23:35.570
they'll have to replace her.

23:35.570 --> 23:38.640
W-Will that really work?

23:41.220 --> 23:42.640
It's mostly luck.

23:47.660 --> 23:48.690
Don't cry.

23:52.750 --> 23:53.740
Passengers who have just boarded,

23:53.740 --> 23:54.870
please move inside!

23:54.940 --> 23:56.590
Take it slow. Be careful.
Don't bump into anything.

23:56.590 --> 23:57.200
Thank you. Thanks.

23:57.200 --> 23:58.860
-Excuse me.
-Tickets for two.

24:08.620 --> 24:09.340
You're tired?

24:09.280 --> 24:11.830
♪ If I want to look far away ♪

24:09.750 --> 24:10.280
I'm okay.

24:14.000 --> 24:16.570
♪ A cloud can't block the sun ♪

24:15.320 --> 24:16.180
[CHUN LAI JIE]

24:16.180 --> 24:17.490
[Develop Campus Services,
Boost Economic Growth]

24:17.700 --> 24:19.270
Your clothes look really beautiful.

24:19.270 --> 24:20.030
Of course!

24:20.030 --> 24:21.500
Our boss picked them all.

24:20.920 --> 24:24.780
♪ Go to the vast sea
with wind and waves ♪

24:26.190 --> 24:29.580
♪ Instead of struggling in the pond ♪

24:30.690 --> 24:33.340
♪ If I have faith in spring ♪

24:35.520 --> 24:38.250
♪ A rainstorm can't bring away
the fragrance of flowers ♪

24:42.660 --> 24:46.380
♪ Those dreams that are hard to realize ♪

24:47.460 --> 24:50.520
♪ Have taken root deep in my heart ♪

24:51.120 --> 24:55.250
♪ After countless times of blooming
and withering, I still plant hope ♪

24:57.870 --> 25:02.120
♪ Seasons change during this trip ♪

25:02.890 --> 25:07.560
♪ Amid the sound of footsteps,
I head into the wind of departure ♪

25:08.170 --> 25:10.220
♪ With youth and innocence ♪

25:10.690 --> 25:12.680
♪ With a faint light ♪

25:13.180 --> 25:16.600
♪ Light up a brighter life ♪

25:17.320 --> 25:21.020
♪ Spring lingers on ♪

25:22.920 --> 25:23.780
Seventy-five.

25:26.120 --> 25:27.750
Also 75. Perfect.

25:28.980 --> 25:30.110
Let me measure this.

25:32.660 --> 25:33.570
Thirty-nine.

25:33.610 --> 25:35.090
Thirty-nine.

25:35.750 --> 25:36.500
Zongbao!

25:37.000 --> 25:38.830
Why did you move my cabinet over there?

25:38.830 --> 25:40.140
Wait. Come on, give me a hand.

25:40.140 --> 25:40.860
No, no, no.

25:40.940 --> 25:41.430
Well...

25:41.550 --> 25:43.210
I... I need it for writing.

25:43.770 --> 25:45.470
I'm setting up a desk for you.

25:45.560 --> 25:46.430
Setting up a...

25:46.700 --> 25:48.010
-Don't bother. This is enough for me.
-No, no, no.

25:48.010 --> 25:49.510
From now... From now on,

25:49.940 --> 25:51.690
we're swapping beds.

25:51.810 --> 25:52.740
You sleep there.

25:53.610 --> 25:54.610
Zongbao, there's no need.

25:54.610 --> 25:55.830
I'm used to sleeping here.

25:55.830 --> 25:57.140
It's fine for me to w-write here.

25:57.140 --> 25:57.920
This is just fine.

25:57.920 --> 26:00.120
You... It's fine for you, but not for us.

26:00.550 --> 26:02.180
Every night, you stay up late

26:02.440 --> 26:04.090
h-here with the light on.

26:04.090 --> 26:05.580
We can't hang on anymore.

26:06.250 --> 26:07.430
Besides, seeing you

26:07.610 --> 26:08.920
sit on the floor

26:08.920 --> 26:10.720
and write all the time over there

26:10.750 --> 26:12.930
makes me feel bad.

26:13.250 --> 26:13.780
You know?

26:13.980 --> 26:16.150
You have to protect your back.

26:16.290 --> 26:16.700
Right?

26:16.700 --> 26:18.580
I just failed to protect my back

26:18.660 --> 26:19.680
at your age.

26:20.160 --> 26:21.360
Come on. Move it over.

26:22.140 --> 26:23.070
Come on.

26:23.220 --> 26:24.190
Give me a hand.

26:24.250 --> 26:24.750
But Zongbao,

26:24.750 --> 26:26.740
Liangliang and Heretic Cao aren't around.

26:26.740 --> 26:27.720
Is this appropriate?

26:27.720 --> 26:29.030
We unanimously

26:29.030 --> 26:31.820
agreed on swapping beds.

26:32.740 --> 26:33.390
I

26:33.510 --> 26:35.380
represent the two of them.

26:36.030 --> 26:36.630
And you are

26:36.750 --> 26:38.810
in charge of execution. Is that fine?

26:39.830 --> 26:41.160
Fine by me!

26:41.160 --> 26:41.610
Fine!

26:41.610 --> 26:42.310
-Fine, right?
-Yes!

26:42.310 --> 26:43.590
Then sit down and try it.

26:43.590 --> 26:44.640
Check the distance.

26:44.640 --> 26:45.680
See if it fits.

26:46.550 --> 26:47.590
Closer. Move a bit closer.

26:47.590 --> 26:48.240
Closer.

26:48.270 --> 26:49.750
Closer.

26:52.070 --> 26:52.950
-Okay.
-Good.

26:53.390 --> 26:54.750
This works. This is good.

26:54.750 --> 26:55.510
From now on,

26:55.510 --> 26:57.240
this will be your little world.

26:59.720 --> 27:00.750
As the old saying goes,

27:00.750 --> 27:02.610
only family enters the same door.

27:02.980 --> 27:03.640
Let me do it.

27:03.640 --> 27:05.600
Conversely,

27:05.900 --> 27:07.010
once you enter the same door,

27:07.010 --> 27:08.290
you'll be family.

27:08.420 --> 27:08.960
Right?

27:09.030 --> 27:10.500
Come on. Swap the beds.

27:11.550 --> 27:12.690
From now on,

27:12.770 --> 27:13.900
you'll be No. 3 here.

27:14.250 --> 27:16.580
Xu Sanli. ("San" means three in Chinese.)

27:16.750 --> 27:18.380
Liangliang and I are the same age.

27:18.380 --> 27:21.050
-He's even several months older than me.
-His psychological age is

27:21.050 --> 27:22.180
younger than yours.

27:23.900 --> 27:24.430
Alright!

27:25.090 --> 27:26.180
Xu Sanli it is!

27:29.180 --> 27:29.900
Mr. Xu!

27:31.770 --> 27:32.500
Mr. Xu!

27:33.010 --> 27:33.810
Give me a hand.

27:37.310 --> 27:38.840
That's nice treatment!

27:38.870 --> 27:40.050
Isn't this the freezer from the store

27:39.420 --> 27:43.720
[Ice lolly & Ice Cream]

27:40.050 --> 27:41.270
by the school's west gate?

27:41.270 --> 27:42.990
Yeah. Push it in a bit.

27:43.870 --> 27:48.400
[Ice lolly & Ice Cream]

27:45.080 --> 27:45.520
I just

27:45.550 --> 27:47.210
wanted to boost our business.

27:47.380 --> 27:48.380
So I rented this

27:48.460 --> 27:49.750
for 10 yuan a day.

27:49.880 --> 27:51.010
The sales go to them.

27:51.050 --> 27:52.570
We just want the foot traffic.

27:52.570 --> 27:53.820
Impressive!

27:53.920 --> 27:56.170
As virtue rises 1 foot, vice rises 10.

27:56.190 --> 27:57.470
Is that a compliment?

27:58.400 --> 28:00.420
Then let's say, as vice rises 1foot,

28:00.680 --> 28:01.400
virtue rises 10.

28:01.400 --> 28:02.380
Just eat.

28:02.570 --> 28:03.940
You've been out in the sun for a while.

28:03.940 --> 28:04.670
Thanks.

28:05.660 --> 28:07.320
Did we sell anything just now?

28:07.380 --> 28:07.810
No.

28:16.510 --> 28:17.310
Why is business

28:17.310 --> 28:18.370
so good over there?

28:18.770 --> 28:19.810
They sell jerseys.

28:19.810 --> 28:20.530
It's the World Cup.

28:20.530 --> 28:21.330
The World Cup?

28:23.030 --> 28:25.830
Does it have anything to do
with our national team?

28:26.590 --> 28:27.450
Good question.

28:27.810 --> 28:29.570
I'll reward you with an ice cream.

28:29.570 --> 28:30.510
I don't want it.

28:30.610 --> 28:31.610
-It's on me.
-I...

28:31.700 --> 28:32.240
My treat.

28:36.550 --> 28:38.480
Spending money before making any.

28:38.510 --> 28:40.170
How much can an ice cream cost?

28:51.900 --> 28:53.630
About your tuition this month,

28:54.310 --> 28:55.640
I actually have an idea.

28:56.900 --> 28:57.640
What idea?

29:00.890 --> 29:01.600
Argentina.

29:04.070 --> 29:04.900
Argentina?

29:05.190 --> 29:05.580
Yes.

29:07.070 --> 29:09.460
How come you still
haven't gotten a role yet?

29:09.460 --> 29:10.860
It's not that easy.

29:11.590 --> 29:12.590
Ranran,

29:12.680 --> 29:14.540
look at you after all these years.

29:14.750 --> 29:15.350
Tell me...

29:16.000 --> 29:17.430
You're all grown up,

29:17.480 --> 29:19.680
but you can't share any of my burden.

29:20.590 --> 29:22.520
I fed you, clothed you,

29:22.550 --> 29:24.900
and supported you to go to Beijing
to make a mark.

29:24.900 --> 29:26.580
Do you think it's easy for me?

29:26.830 --> 29:27.500
Mom,

29:28.200 --> 29:29.350
this is Beijing.

29:29.350 --> 29:30.500
I'm a new actress.

29:30.500 --> 29:32.330
It's hard for me to get roles.

29:32.470 --> 29:33.270
Well,

29:33.590 --> 29:34.510
over the years,

29:34.560 --> 29:36.310
I've spent so much money

29:36.380 --> 29:37.750
on your acting classes!

29:38.310 --> 29:39.480
Don't tell me

29:39.480 --> 29:40.400
this was a losing deal

29:40.400 --> 29:41.930
now that you're in Beijing!

29:42.180 --> 29:43.380
You money pit.

29:43.630 --> 29:44.960
I'm not a money pit.

29:44.960 --> 29:46.660
You're calling me that again.

29:49.010 --> 29:50.480
How about this? I'll pay the rent

29:50.480 --> 29:51.050
for this month

29:51.050 --> 29:52.420
and then go back to Huzhou
to work in the factory.

29:52.420 --> 29:53.150
Is that okay?

29:53.440 --> 29:54.500
Alright, alright.

29:54.810 --> 29:56.010
This is the last time.

30:08.590 --> 30:09.350
Sir, you got your jerseys

30:09.350 --> 30:10.480
from a street stall, didn't you?

30:10.480 --> 30:11.610
It's too expensive!

30:11.790 --> 30:12.380
Give me a discount.

30:12.380 --> 30:13.090
I'll buy it if it's cheaper.

30:13.090 --> 30:14.330
Look at this. Look.

30:14.380 --> 30:15.960
This is the real deal
made for export and sold locally.

30:15.960 --> 30:17.010
I just got these from the Port of Tianjin.

30:17.010 --> 30:17.680
yesterday.

30:17.770 --> 30:18.460
Shipped from the Port of Tianjin?

30:18.460 --> 30:20.000
Yes! You think 35 yuan per piece is

30:20.000 --> 30:20.590
too pricey?

30:20.590 --> 30:21.460
It's not expensive at all!

30:21.460 --> 30:22.050
How about 33?

30:22.050 --> 30:23.050
I'll take 2 pieces for 33 yuan each.

30:23.050 --> 30:24.030
I want one! Give me one!

30:24.030 --> 30:25.040
I want to buy it!

30:25.110 --> 30:26.770
You want to sell jerseys, too?

30:27.700 --> 30:29.830
Yes, and only the Argentina team ones.

30:30.220 --> 30:34.970
[Ice lolly & Ice Cream]

30:31.400 --> 30:32.530
I have connections.

30:32.570 --> 30:33.900
I know someone at the factory.

30:33.900 --> 30:34.750
That's great.

30:34.850 --> 30:36.550
Wait, only Argentina?

30:37.140 --> 30:39.250
This is our star product.

30:39.740 --> 30:40.640
Don't you know?

30:40.770 --> 30:41.770
This year's hot favorite

30:41.770 --> 30:42.900
to win is Argentina.

30:43.500 --> 30:44.830
Do you know Maradona?

30:44.980 --> 30:46.080
Maradona?

30:46.240 --> 30:47.720
Sounds like Malatang.

30:48.160 --> 30:49.480
It's "Maradona."

30:51.480 --> 30:52.120
Look.

30:52.960 --> 30:54.740
So many people are buying them now.

30:54.740 --> 30:56.120
We're already late.

30:56.770 --> 30:58.300
To rake in profits in one go,

30:58.570 --> 30:59.570
we have to be bold.

30:59.760 --> 31:05.800
[Ice lolly & Ice Cream]

31:00.250 --> 31:01.310
The last World Cup.

31:01.840 --> 31:03.040
In the last World Cup,

31:03.110 --> 31:04.770
Argentina was the runner-up.

31:05.180 --> 31:07.210
They're really hungry for victory now.

31:07.210 --> 31:09.140
Maradona is

31:10.160 --> 31:11.160
on fire this year.

31:11.460 --> 31:12.860
Is that your inside info?

31:14.900 --> 31:16.230
Han Qiaosheng also said so.

31:16.230 --> 31:17.420
Who is Han Qiaosheng?

31:17.420 --> 31:18.380
A football commentator.

31:18.380 --> 31:19.880
Then why are you whispering?

31:19.880 --> 31:21.010
Doesn't the whole country know that then?

31:21.010 --> 31:21.640
Exactly.

31:21.680 --> 31:22.940
I-I just felt that it fit the vibe

31:22.940 --> 31:24.400
b-between the three of us.

31:25.820 --> 31:33.590
[Ice lolly & Ice Cream]

31:26.750 --> 31:27.160
Look.

31:27.810 --> 31:29.880
There are a lot of student football fans.

31:29.880 --> 31:32.610
I think we should only sell jerseys then.

31:32.920 --> 31:33.550
I promise

31:34.140 --> 31:36.070
we'll make our money back overnight.

31:36.070 --> 31:36.960
Since you put it that way,

31:36.960 --> 31:38.110
should I stock a few, too?

31:38.110 --> 31:38.970
Sure.

31:40.030 --> 31:41.480
I sell women's clothing.

31:41.980 --> 31:43.850
Then you'll miss the chance

31:43.870 --> 31:44.870
to make a fortune.

31:45.330 --> 31:46.700
Do you think I'm a money-grubber?

31:46.700 --> 31:47.700
I'll make the call for you right now

31:47.700 --> 31:48.560
to carry it out.

31:48.940 --> 31:49.350
Nice!

31:50.070 --> 31:51.000
Thank you, miss!

31:52.920 --> 31:55.180
Do we really only get the Argentina ones?

32:02.460 --> 32:02.920
Fine.

32:21.000 --> 32:21.640
Hey, girl.

32:22.180 --> 32:22.980
What's wrong?

32:23.610 --> 32:24.470
Are you crying?

32:26.050 --> 32:27.450
D-Did someone bully you?

32:27.900 --> 32:29.360
I'm rehearsing in my head.

32:30.480 --> 32:31.880
Rehearsing in your head?

32:32.550 --> 32:33.400
If you ask me,

32:33.810 --> 32:35.700
you don't even need to do it.

32:36.530 --> 32:38.410
Your every expression is

32:38.570 --> 32:39.650
full of drama.

32:41.000 --> 32:42.290
Even you can tell

32:42.290 --> 32:43.840
that I'm a natural actress.

32:44.920 --> 32:46.860
That director is just blind.

32:48.250 --> 32:49.100
S-So...

32:49.270 --> 32:51.390
So you failed to get the role?

32:51.830 --> 32:53.270
It's okay, girl.

32:53.700 --> 32:55.310
Do you know

32:55.640 --> 32:58.990
h-how many movies
the film studio makes a year?

32:59.140 --> 33:00.520
Dozens.

33:00.830 --> 33:01.900
If this one doesn't work out,

33:01.900 --> 33:03.300
w-we'll get the next one.

33:04.290 --> 33:06.430
Several movies, and not one picked me.

33:06.570 --> 33:07.080
No,

33:07.610 --> 33:09.070
that's not what I meant.

33:09.290 --> 33:09.880
Girl,

33:10.050 --> 33:12.040
when w-we act,

33:12.180 --> 33:14.240
w-we can't only fixate on those roles,

33:14.240 --> 33:15.370
the ones with lines.

33:15.790 --> 33:17.700
Let's look at the ones without lines.

33:17.700 --> 33:18.290
Right?

33:18.420 --> 33:19.960
Just think about... about...

33:19.960 --> 33:20.980
life.

33:21.160 --> 33:22.760
It's about 30,000 days long.

33:22.980 --> 33:24.780
The key is to experience, right?

33:24.780 --> 33:26.140
Y-You should try to experience

33:26.140 --> 33:27.940
the ones without lines, like...

33:28.110 --> 33:29.580
Like a corpse, right?

33:29.660 --> 33:31.180
Or someone hanging themselves.

33:31.180 --> 33:31.850
Or those buried alive...

33:31.850 --> 33:33.880
Can you please
think of something better for me?

33:33.880 --> 33:35.540
Yes, yes, there are good ones.

33:35.610 --> 33:37.290
Right. Then let's p-play roles with lines.

33:37.290 --> 33:39.040
L-Let's do the... the...

33:39.180 --> 33:40.380
The fighting scenes.

33:40.400 --> 33:41.510
Those shooting guns, right?

33:41.510 --> 33:44.070
Let's play servants to the Emperor

33:44.550 --> 33:45.510
or the Empress.

33:45.510 --> 33:46.710
Come, Your Highness.

33:46.740 --> 33:48.410
The steps are too high.

33:48.440 --> 33:49.680
C-Come on down.

33:49.830 --> 33:50.500
Your Highness.

33:50.500 --> 33:51.310
Come on. Come down.

33:51.310 --> 33:52.000
No, I won't go down.

33:52.000 --> 33:52.660
Come down, come down.

33:52.660 --> 33:53.900
Come on, come down now.

33:53.900 --> 33:54.960
Come down, come on.

33:55.480 --> 33:56.680
What's going on here?

33:57.640 --> 33:58.400
Guo,

33:58.900 --> 34:00.050
don't get fresh.

34:00.050 --> 34:01.230
You have a family.

34:01.380 --> 34:03.220
What are you talking about? You...

34:03.220 --> 34:04.380
This girl... Well...

34:04.380 --> 34:05.840
Um, she went to an audition

34:05.850 --> 34:07.140
and didn't get the role.

34:07.140 --> 34:09.639
I was just comforting her.

34:16.480 --> 34:17.940
I thought it was a big deal.

34:18.210 --> 34:20.070
So it's just that the director
didn't pick you.

34:20.070 --> 34:21.530
We didn't like him either!

34:21.860 --> 34:23.130
If not this time, then next time.

34:23.130 --> 34:23.530
Right.

34:23.800 --> 34:25.659
You have to learn from Guo on this.

34:25.860 --> 34:26.719
Look at Mr. Guo.

34:27.030 --> 34:27.800
He's been waiting at the gate

34:27.800 --> 34:28.570
of the film studio for years.

34:28.570 --> 34:29.460
What roles has he played?

34:29.460 --> 34:31.340
He hasn't gotten a single role as well!

34:31.340 --> 34:32.820
But he has a good mindset. Look.

34:32.820 --> 34:33.719
Nice and plump.

34:33.860 --> 34:34.190
Look.

34:34.230 --> 34:36.190
I-It's mainly

34:36.280 --> 34:37.800
because of my back problems, right?

34:37.800 --> 34:39.000
I dare not exercise, right?

34:39.000 --> 34:40.000
It's because you're chill.

34:40.000 --> 34:40.530
Chill.

34:40.900 --> 34:42.360
How many years has it been?

34:43.260 --> 34:44.460
Then wouldn't I...

34:46.300 --> 34:48.429
Then I'm even more hopeless, aren't I?

34:48.690 --> 34:49.500
Girl, girl!

34:49.590 --> 34:51.420
Girl, that's not what I meant.

34:51.500 --> 34:52.630
What I'm saying is,

34:52.630 --> 34:54.190
don't compare yourself
to people better off than you.

34:54.190 --> 34:55.710
Compare yourself to those worse off!

34:55.710 --> 34:57.130
What are you talking about?

34:57.130 --> 34:58.940
Look at the people living in the basement.

34:58.940 --> 35:00.780
Who among them doesn't feel frustrated?

35:00.780 --> 35:02.570
Every single one of them aims high,

35:02.570 --> 35:03.830
but has a fragile fate.

35:04.860 --> 35:05.930
Well, he... he...

35:05.980 --> 35:07.790
Well, he's frustrated too!

35:08.130 --> 35:09.530
I... I'm not frustrated.

35:10.030 --> 35:11.830
Why wouldn't you be frustrated?

35:13.400 --> 35:14.670
Right, I'm frustrated too!

35:14.670 --> 35:15.600
I'm frustrated!

35:15.780 --> 35:16.960
What are you frustrated about?

35:16.960 --> 35:17.340
I...

35:18.090 --> 35:19.110
He... What am I frustrated about?

35:19.110 --> 35:19.550
He...

35:19.940 --> 35:21.260
He... well...

35:21.400 --> 35:22.890
When the boss comes,

35:22.980 --> 35:24.250
his face...

35:24.380 --> 35:26.300
faces the boss like this.

35:27.300 --> 35:28.610
But when the boss turns away,

35:28.610 --> 35:30.010
his face changes to this.

35:30.230 --> 35:30.800
Right?

35:32.380 --> 35:33.610
Look, she smiled. Look.

35:33.610 --> 35:34.400
Come down, come down.

35:34.400 --> 35:35.230
Come down, come down.

35:35.230 --> 35:36.170
I'm fine!

35:40.340 --> 35:41.460
Do you two think

35:41.460 --> 35:42.650
I'm going to die here?

35:42.650 --> 35:43.190
If I were to jump,

35:43.190 --> 35:43.960
I wouldn't die

35:43.960 --> 35:45.050
in this courtyard.

35:45.150 --> 35:46.570
This... this looks pretty dangerous.

35:46.570 --> 35:47.030
You...

35:47.090 --> 35:49.190
I just wanted to look at the sky

35:49.300 --> 35:50.900
and get some fresh air.

35:51.570 --> 35:52.940
That's more like it, girl.

35:52.940 --> 35:53.730
Even if we jump,

35:53.730 --> 35:54.490
we shouldn't do in this courtyard.

35:54.490 --> 35:55.610
Jump in someone else's courtyard.

35:55.610 --> 35:56.800
-You...
-What are you saying?

35:56.800 --> 35:57.570
Look.

35:57.900 --> 35:59.570
I have a chilled watermelon over there.

35:59.570 --> 36:00.550
I'll cut it open.

36:00.780 --> 36:01.570
Let's have some watermelon.

36:01.570 --> 36:03.290
-Let's not stay out here in the sun.
- Have some watermelon!

36:03.290 --> 36:04.670
I'll come down and eat later.

36:04.670 --> 36:06.260
I want to stay here a little longer.

36:06.260 --> 36:07.260
You guys go ahead.

36:07.280 --> 36:08.480
Okay, come down soon!

36:08.650 --> 36:10.030
I'll go cut the watermelon.

36:10.030 --> 36:10.910
It's all right.

36:11.440 --> 36:12.500
Don't cry anymore.

36:14.570 --> 36:15.300
Go on, get busy.

36:15.300 --> 36:16.260
Wipe your tears.

36:17.110 --> 36:17.910
It's all gone.

36:18.070 --> 36:19.270
If anything happens,

36:19.440 --> 36:20.340
tell me.

36:22.730 --> 36:23.460
Look at this.

36:23.690 --> 36:25.070
You scared me so much,

36:25.190 --> 36:28.190
my clothes got all wrinkled up
from me clutching them.

36:32.860 --> 36:34.120
Have some watermelon!

36:40.280 --> 36:41.300
Sit a bit lower.

36:41.300 --> 36:41.940
Lower, lower.

36:41.940 --> 36:43.130
Can this outfit sell well?

36:43.130 --> 36:44.400
Of course we can, why not?

36:44.400 --> 36:45.030
After getting my hair cut,

36:45.030 --> 36:45.610
it just feels like...

36:45.610 --> 36:47.300
I permed my hair for him.

36:47.300 --> 36:48.800
I permed it, and he cut his hair.

36:48.800 --> 36:49.670
What are you even talking about?

36:49.670 --> 36:51.010
Has the livestream started?

36:51.010 --> 36:52.090
Just started, just started.

36:52.090 --> 36:52.570
Hurry.

36:55.820 --> 36:57.460
Where did you get these clothes?

36:57.460 --> 36:58.610
We sourced them ourselves.

36:58.610 --> 36:59.650
You two must be turning heads everywhere.

36:59.650 --> 37:00.820
This is so cool!

37:00.820 --> 37:01.940
Of course!

37:01.940 --> 37:02.670
Do you have more?

37:02.670 --> 37:03.400
Don't touch!

37:03.590 --> 37:04.840
Argentina is really trending right now.

37:04.840 --> 37:05.710
They sell one of these outside for

37:05.710 --> 37:07.190
forty or fifty.

37:07.380 --> 37:09.050
Are you charging us?

37:09.090 --> 37:10.260
What else would we do?

37:10.260 --> 37:11.010
How much?

37:12.820 --> 37:14.010
The, the cost price...

37:14.010 --> 37:14.530
Fine.

37:14.940 --> 37:15.650
Thirty-five.

37:15.650 --> 37:17.260
Thirty-five is the cost price!

37:17.260 --> 37:18.720
Thirty-five?

37:19.360 --> 37:20.550
Are you crazy?

37:20.550 --> 37:21.530
Forget it if you don't want it. Here.

37:21.530 --> 37:22.400
I'll take one. I'll take one.

37:22.400 --> 37:23.000
You want one?

37:23.000 --> 37:23.530
I'll take one.

37:23.530 --> 37:24.630
You... you want number 10?

37:24.630 --> 37:25.500
What can I do? I like it.

37:25.500 --> 37:26.270
Right?

37:26.690 --> 37:27.600
He's my idol.

37:28.110 --> 37:28.710
Here, here.

37:28.710 --> 37:29.570
Okay, okay, okay.

37:29.570 --> 37:30.970
All eyes on him this year.

37:31.170 --> 37:31.700
Shengli.

37:32.150 --> 37:33.900
I... I want one too.

37:33.900 --> 37:35.430
Then take one. Pay me later.

37:35.780 --> 37:36.190
Okay.

37:39.090 --> 37:39.420
What's wrong?

37:39.420 --> 37:40.460
He doesn't have money, but I do.

37:40.460 --> 37:41.000
Get me one!

37:41.000 --> 37:42.460
Sell... sell it first, sell it first.

37:42.460 --> 37:42.990
Alright.

37:43.190 --> 37:43.840
Get me one too.

37:43.840 --> 37:45.240
You too? You want one too?

37:45.630 --> 37:46.880
Perfect, no need for change.

37:46.880 --> 37:47.860
You look like a basketball player.

37:47.860 --> 37:48.400
Who else wants one?

37:48.400 --> 37:49.980
Zhuang Zhuang, I'll take one too.

37:49.980 --> 37:50.590
Get me one as well.

37:50.590 --> 37:51.230
-Okay!
-Two pieces, right?

37:51.230 --> 37:52.560
Two pieces. Two pieces.

37:52.920 --> 37:53.720
Here, take it.

37:55.110 --> 37:56.110
It's starting!

37:56.110 --> 37:57.500
-The quality's really good.
-Come to me if you need more.

37:57.500 --> 37:58.250
Of course.

37:58.320 --> 37:59.250
Plenty in stock!

38:01.320 --> 38:02.050
How is it?

38:02.130 --> 38:03.670
I told you it would work.

38:03.710 --> 38:04.820
They really sell.

38:05.000 --> 38:05.650
Xu.

38:05.760 --> 38:07.090
Let me get one on credit.

38:07.090 --> 38:08.710
On credit? Not a chance.

38:08.710 --> 38:09.910
Just watch your game.

38:10.570 --> 38:11.480
You should get number 9.

38:11.480 --> 38:13.280
You kind of look like Batistuta.

38:16.360 --> 38:18.220
You two like watching soccer too?

38:19.210 --> 38:20.800
We do now.

38:21.760 --> 38:22.230
Nice.

38:22.840 --> 38:23.960
Good taste.

38:24.300 --> 38:26.230
No wonder you two are making money.

38:31.000 --> 38:32.030
We have so much stock.

38:32.030 --> 38:34.340
Should we borrow a vehicle
to transport it?

38:34.340 --> 38:36.440
A bike would be convenient.

38:39.860 --> 38:41.390
I'll borrow a bike from you.

38:43.110 --> 38:44.190
For the sake of these clothes,

38:44.190 --> 38:44.940
take the bike and use it.

38:44.940 --> 38:47.010
You're doing this for my clothes? You...

38:47.010 --> 38:47.960
For the clothes.

38:51.090 --> 38:51.860
Nice shot!

38:53.280 --> 38:53.820
So close.

38:57.610 --> 38:58.980
Yes. Hold it there.

38:59.670 --> 39:00.600
Okay. It's back.

39:01.500 --> 39:03.630
-Okay, okay, don't move!
-Don't move.

39:06.130 --> 39:06.960
Oh my god!

39:07.420 --> 39:08.480
No, just stand there and don't move.

39:08.480 --> 39:09.860
You don't... Just stand there.

39:09.860 --> 39:10.880
Maradona, that's him.

39:10.880 --> 39:11.460
That's him.

39:11.460 --> 39:12.030
I can't just

39:12.030 --> 39:13.490
stand here forever, can I?

39:14.050 --> 39:14.850
Wait a second.

39:15.070 --> 39:16.400
You're going to snap it.

39:16.530 --> 39:18.130
Alright, alright, alright.

39:18.280 --> 39:19.010
Much better.

39:19.820 --> 39:20.820
There's a replay.

39:24.110 --> 39:24.940
He's down.

39:25.170 --> 39:26.760
This should be a throw-in, right?

39:26.760 --> 39:27.170
No.

39:27.230 --> 39:28.210
This should be a free kick.

39:28.210 --> 39:29.410
That's a yellow card.

39:35.150 --> 39:36.210
What's that about?

39:36.440 --> 39:37.500
What's that about?

39:39.940 --> 39:40.900
Disgusting!

39:41.170 --> 39:42.150
So disgusting!

39:42.460 --> 39:45.300
[Seasons Change Hostel]

39:46.460 --> 39:48.130
So disgusting!

39:50.590 --> 39:52.340
[Seasons Change Hostel]

39:59.980 --> 40:00.770
Again!

40:32.050 --> 40:33.780
Yeah, I don't have class today.

40:33.860 --> 40:34.870
Is the shop busy?

40:35.480 --> 40:36.280
Not too bad.

40:36.550 --> 40:38.280
You're running low on tuition, aren't you?

40:38.280 --> 40:38.780
I didn't expect

40:38.780 --> 40:40.640
to have so many classes each week.

40:41.190 --> 40:42.920
I'll wire you some money tomorrow.

40:42.920 --> 40:43.790
Don't worry.

40:44.340 --> 40:45.960
If the teacher is willing to
give you extra lessons,

40:45.960 --> 40:47.090
that's a good thing.

40:47.230 --> 40:48.090
No need.

40:49.510 --> 40:50.280
I—

40:50.320 --> 40:51.840
I'm running a stall with a friend now.

40:51.840 --> 40:53.100
We've made some money.

40:53.440 --> 40:54.220
A friend?

40:54.650 --> 40:55.920
Where is this friend from?

40:55.920 --> 40:57.050
A friend in Beijing.

40:57.760 --> 40:58.890
A friend in Beijing?

41:00.340 --> 41:01.540
Do you know them well?

41:01.780 --> 41:02.920
When you're away from home,

41:02.920 --> 41:04.050
safety comes first.

41:04.050 --> 41:06.050
You don't need to worry about money.

41:06.230 --> 41:07.190
I'm all grown up now.

41:07.190 --> 41:08.450
I can earn my own money.

41:09.300 --> 41:09.920
My mom

41:10.110 --> 41:12.420
makes beautiful clothes, and I sell them.

41:12.420 --> 41:14.670
Like mother, like daughter.

41:16.610 --> 41:17.210
By the way,

41:17.710 --> 41:19.300
the girl I live with

41:19.300 --> 41:20.940
keeps saying my clothes look great,

41:20.940 --> 41:22.530
and that I've got good taste.

41:22.530 --> 41:24.460
I told her it's all thanks to my mom.

41:26.130 --> 41:27.190
Alright, alright.

41:27.280 --> 41:28.600
I can't out-talk you.

41:29.360 --> 41:31.020
But don't overwork yourself.

41:31.050 --> 41:32.520
Take it easy, okay?

41:32.730 --> 41:33.460
Don't worry.

41:34.090 --> 41:35.690
Are you and Uncle doing well?

41:36.380 --> 41:37.670
We're both fine.

41:37.730 --> 41:38.930
Don't worry about us.

41:40.940 --> 41:42.550
Alright, I have to go now.

41:42.980 --> 41:44.110
Don't send me money.

41:44.280 --> 41:45.480
Take care of yourself,

41:45.480 --> 41:47.080
and send my regards to Uncle.

41:47.150 --> 41:47.530
Also,

41:47.800 --> 41:49.880
when will the home phone be installed?

41:49.880 --> 41:51.860
Soon, we've already booked the technician.

41:51.860 --> 41:53.110
He'll come install it in a few days.

41:53.110 --> 41:54.630
It'll be more convenient then.

41:54.630 --> 41:56.070
You can call home,

41:56.070 --> 41:57.000
or call the shop.

41:57.380 --> 41:58.860
If anything happens, tell us right away.

41:58.860 --> 41:59.420
Got it?

41:59.630 --> 42:00.820
Okay, got it, got it.

42:01.190 --> 42:01.900
Make sure you eat well,

42:01.900 --> 42:02.760
and take care of yourself.

42:02.760 --> 42:03.440
Okay, okay, okay.

42:03.440 --> 42:04.370
Go get busy then.

42:09.090 --> 42:09.690
From home?

42:10.260 --> 42:10.800
My mom.

42:11.420 --> 42:13.350
You're really close with your mom.

42:13.460 --> 42:14.480
She nags a lot too.

42:15.590 --> 42:16.000
You...

42:17.000 --> 42:17.930
I'm heading out.

42:18.150 --> 42:19.410
I'm meeting Mr. Cui

42:19.460 --> 42:20.920
to talk about meeting a director.

42:20.920 --> 42:21.760
Then hurry up and go.

42:21.760 --> 42:22.590
I'm off then.

42:22.860 --> 42:23.510
Good luck.

42:28.360 --> 42:29.020
Well,

42:29.380 --> 42:30.820
besides the two thousand,

42:30.820 --> 42:32.530
I'll wire her

42:32.530 --> 42:33.460
the five hundred

42:33.570 --> 42:34.900
from the shop register.

42:35.800 --> 42:37.460
No need, she still has some.

42:37.650 --> 42:38.650
Let's send the money

42:38.650 --> 42:39.510
month by month.

42:40.050 --> 42:41.820
If a girl carries too much money,

42:41.820 --> 42:43.280
she might attract trouble.

42:43.280 --> 42:44.590
Two thousand isn't enough.

42:44.590 --> 42:47.320
She must be short on money
but too afraid to say so.

42:47.500 --> 42:48.230
It's enough.

42:48.400 --> 42:49.460
I've done the math.

42:51.000 --> 42:53.800
I feel more at ease
when she has some extra money on hand.

42:53.800 --> 42:55.260
I'm going to wire it to her.

42:56.300 --> 42:56.670
You...
